import React from 'react';
 
const QnAList = props => {
  return (
    <>
      <QnATable headersName={['글번호', '제목', '등록일', '조회수']}>
        <QnATableRow>
          <QnATableColumn>1</QnATableColumn>
          <QnATableColumn>첫번째 게시글입니다.</QnATableColumn>
          <QnATableColumn>2020-10-25</QnATableColumn>
          <QnATableColumn>6</QnATableColumn>
        </QnATableRow>
        <QnATableRow>
          <QnATableColumn>2</QnATableColumn>
          <QnATableColumn>두번째 게시글입니다.</QnATableColumn>
          <QnATableColumn>2020-10-25</QnATableColumn>
          <QnATableColumn>5</QnATableColumn>
        </QnATableRow>
        <QnATableRow>
          <QnATableColumn>3</QnATableColumn>
          <QnATableColumn>세번째 게시글입니다.</QnATableColumn>
          <QnATableColumn>2020-10-25</QnATableColumn>
          <QnATableColumn>1</QnATableColumn>
        </QnATableRow>
        <QnATableRow>
          <QnATableColumn>4</QnATableColumn>
          <QnATableColumn>네번째 게시글입니다.</QnATableColumn>
          <QnATableColumn>2020-10-25</QnATableColumn>
          <QnATableColumn>2</QnATableColumn>
        </QnATableRow>
        <QnATableRow>
          <QnATableColumn>5</QnATableColumn>
          <QnATableColumn>다섯번째 게시글입니다.</QnATableColumn>
          <QnATableColumn>2020-10-25</QnATableColumn>
          <QnATableColumn>4</QnATableColumn>
        </QnATableRow>
      </QnATable>
    </>
  )
}
 
export default QnAList;
